<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-47-1234 </DOCNO><TEXT>On the basis of literary data and clinical examination (112 patients)methods of clinical radiodiagnosis of metastases of central lung cancerin regional lymph nodes using computers are developed. Methods are testedon control clinical material (110 patients). Using computers (Bayes andVald methods) 57.3% and 65.5% correct answers correspondingly are obtained,that is by 14.6% and 22.8% higher the level of clinical diagnosis ofmetastases. Diagnostic errors are analysed. Complexes of clinical-radiologicalsigns of symptoms of metastases are outlined. 6 refs.; 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>